**Lynch** | Poll
Available Options: @All, Cancel
Allowed Voters: @All
Hammer: Yes
Passive Start Day: Create Poll in #voting_booth [Temporal: Day 1+]
On Poll Closed:
  • Lynch @Winner
  • Announce `@Winner was lynched.`

__Formalized__
On Vote Change: Announce @Voter changed vote to @NewVoteText
On Vote Add: Announce @Voter voted @VoteText
On Vote Remove: Announce @Voter unvoted @VoteText
